----------------------------------------------
Version 4.4 Beta 1  18.08.98
----------------------------------------------

Changed Layout

- Replaced the buttons "Save to xxx" with "Save File-Id to archive"
  Supported archives: DMS,LHA,LZX,ARC,ZOO,TAR/TGZ and ZIP. 

- Changes on: Rename,Delete,Move,Copy and Delete Archive Item.
  Cursor will stay at the selected position...

- Optimized Delete Archive Item code.

- Finished code for "Hidden file"

- Created new "Public" version

----------------------------------------------
Version 4.4 Beta 2  19.08.98
----------------------------------------------

Changed Layout


- Added "MakeDir" Button

- Added "Guide to HTML" Button
  This will convert AmigaGuide files to HTML.  (25%)

- Added new (test)code for the file selection. (20%)
  AmigaGuide files must clicked twice to show the guide.
  Doubleclick for Directories too. (now you can delete,move,copy whole dirs...)

----------------------------------------------
Version 4.4 Beta 3  20.08.98
----------------------------------------------

- Removed filesize bug (old) ! -Fuck-
  If you selected a file with the filesize of 0 bytes the Explorer closed the session.
  Now you will get informed that there is an corrupted file...

